Source: dfatmo
Section: libs
Priority: extra
Maintainer: Andreas Auras <yak54@inkennet.de>
Uploaders: Wolfgang Mangold <vdr@gmx.de>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 9), cdbs, pkg-config, zip, libusb-1.0-0-dev, python-dev, libxine2-dev, vdr-dev (>= 2.2.0)
Standards-Version: 3.9.5

Package: dfatmo
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libxine-dfatmo-plugin
Description: DFAtmo the driver for 'Atmolight' controllers for VDR, XBMC and xinelib based video players
 The DFAtmo driver analyze the video picture and generates
 output data for so called 'Atmolight' controllers.
 This package contains the native Python DFAtmo driver module, the native DFAtmo output drivers and
 the DFAtmo XBMC addon installation zip file.

Package: libxine-dfatmo-plugin
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, dfatmo
Description: DFAtmo the driver for 'Atmolight' controllers for VDR, XBMC and xinelib based video players
 The DFAtmo xinelib post plugin analyze the video picture and generates
 output data for so called "atmolight" controllers.
 This package contains the DfAtmo xinelib post plugin.

Package: vdr-plugin-dfatmo
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, dfatmo
Description: DFAtmo the driver for 'Atmolight' controllers for VDR, XBMC and xinelib based video players
 The DFAtmo xinelib post plugin analyze the video picture and generates
 output data for so called "atmolight" controllers.
 This package contains the DfAtmo VDR plugin.
